  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.mp4?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello Mr.President!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soak in the stench of the Oval Office while you get to work on your very important tasks. There’s a lot of work that needs to get done, which is why you have your entirely disposable agents at your service. And the sooner you’re done with work, the sooner we can hit the fairways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUT WATCH OUT.</strong> Not everyone who walks in can be trusted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SO WAKE UP</strong> and grab your revolver. You've got a country to serve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/329aa36cea025bb514c907cc3342fbbe.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/329aa36cea025bb514c907cc3342fbbe.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/329aa36cea025bb514c907cc3342fbbe.mp4?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each day, you sit behind the Resolute Desk while you complete your tasks:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer calls from world leaders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage the most powerful economy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sign critical executive orders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Read through top secret documents</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/4480c0d7f59c0150dacab0df97f0cf16.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/4480c0d7f59c0150dacab0df97f0cf16.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/4480c0d7f59c0150dacab0df97f0cf16.mp4?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a demanding job, a hard job. It makes you want to take a nap. But taking a nap around insolent staff like this is dangerous. So remember to drink water and bonk your head to stay awake. Each day brings more work to do, so you have to be fast. Learn to multitask while keeping an eye out for danger and you should be fine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/f942c99c8323fedbe628a349e8ccbdf2.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/f942c99c8323fedbe628a349e8ccbdf2.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/f942c99c8323fedbe628a349e8ccbdf2.mp4?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/d5ea2811cd988682d2c9c308a08a387e.mp4?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello Mr.President!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soak in the stench of the Oval Office while you get to work on your very important tasks. There’s a lot of work that needs to get done, which is why you have your entirely disposable agents at your service. And the sooner you’re done with work, the sooner we can hit the fairways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUT WATCH OUT.</strong> Not everyone who walks in can be trusted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SO WAKE UP</strong> and grab your revolver. You've got a country to serve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/329aa36cea025bb514c907cc3342fbbe.poster.avif?t=1773686324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4364570/extras/329aa36cea025bb514c907cc3342fbbe.webm?t=1773686324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co